  "text": "In line with a previous study which included three graded systems (Stars, Smileys and Health Protector Factor), along with MTL, GDA and a simple summary format, we found that the graded label (i.e. 5-CNL) was the label format which exhibited the best effectiveness across product categories [CITATION_1] .",
